location.fullValue: Majesty Plan, Black Rock at Verrado

data.description: Pride of ownership is shown in this 4-bedroom property in the desirable Verrado Community! It flaunts stone accents, a lovely front yard, a 2-car garage, & a delightful front porch, ideal for morning coffee. Be impressed by the beautiful interior boasting high ceilings, a trending palette, & wood-plank tile flooring. The formal living & dining rooms and spacious family room are perfect for relaxing & entertaining guests. The gourmet eat-in kitchen includes SS appliances, recessed lighting, quartz counters, a walk-in pantry, staggered wood cabinetry, a breakfast bar, & a breakfast nook. Double doors open to a carpeted main suite offering a bay window, a full bathroom w/dual vanities, & a walk-in closet The home's elegance extends outdoors in the side patio & backyard, showcasing a fountain, a covered patio w/pavers underfoot, & lush lawn. This gem won't disappoint!
